bug.short_desc: "provider" Job does not list "qx.Bootstrap" in dependency file

long_desc.thetext:
If a code provider is generated from the framework itself the "dependencies.json" does not list the "qx/Bootstrap" as dependency.
--snip-- // run in the "framework" folder ./generate.py provider --snip--
The "dependencies.json" does list the "qx/Bootstrap" as "run"/"load" dependency, but the "qx/Bootstrap" itself is not listed.
Created attachment 758 Dependencies file which does not list the qx/Bootstrap entry
Created attachment 759 configuration used to generate the framework code provider
